  "body": "## Description\r\n*Type*: Bug\r\n\r\nUser identifier (display, random or ENS name) are not highlighted enough, that makes it hard to scan the list of messages and identify who is saying what.\r\n\r\n<img width=\"680\" alt=\"captura de pantalla 2018-12-05 a la s 7 35 41 p m\" src=\"https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/37297779/49548612-0f13c600-f8c5-11e8-8081-005a5a640ce4.png\">\r\n\r\n## Expected behavior\r\nPrimary identifier (display name, random name or ENS name) should be highlighted using the correct styles.\r\n\r\n<img width=\"527\" alt=\"captura de pantalla 2018-12-05 a la s 7 46 26 p m\" src=\"https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/37297779/49549095-80a04400-f8c6-11e8-8e04-0a563d07c364.png\">\r\n\r\n## Solution\r\n- [ ] Include InterUI semibold](https://rsms.me/inter/) (font-weight: 600) to our library\r\n- [ ] Highlight main user identifier in chat area[ following the correct styles ](https://www.figma.com/file/MRYBI5axcTwL4Ft8xAYhFOfy/Desktop?node-id=728%3A41)\r\n\r\n[See designs on Figma](https://www.figma.com/file/MRYBI5axcTwL4Ft8xAYhFOfy/Desktop?node-id=728%3A41)\r\n\n\n<blockquote><img src=\"https://rsms.me/inter/res/poster.png\" width=\"48\" align=\"right\"><div><img src=\"/inter/res/favicon.png\" height=\"14\"> rsms.me/inter</div><div><strong><a href=\"https://rsms.me/inter//\">Inter UI font family</a></strong></div><div>Inter UI is a new typeface optimized for computer user interfaces</div></blockquote>",
